## PRIORITY GUIDE (REMINDER)

- **H** — blocks multi-tenant scale, actively causing bugs, or blocks an in-flight session
- **M** — must fix before second publisher goes live
- **L** — nice-to-have, low risk, costs very little to defer

Priority reflects **cost of NOT fixing.** "Quick fix available" is not priority — something can be high priority and hard to fix, or low priority and trivial.

